high_descs: Turn right and walk one step then turn left and walk to the small table to the right of the bookshelf.
Pick up the pencil that's on the edge of the shelf in front of you.
Turn right and take a step so you are facing the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk under the tissue box all the way to the right of the other two tissue boxes.
Turn around and walk to the door then turn right.
Pick up the pencil that's on the edge of the top of the bookshelf.
Turn right and walk back to the desk.
Lay the pencil on the tissue box to the right of the other two so it is touching both the pencil and the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Place two pencils on the desk.

high_descs: Walk ahead and slightly right to the end table.
Pick up the pencil from the shelf
Turn right.
Place the pencil on the desk in front of the rightmost tissue box.
Turn around and take a few steps to the book case.
Pick the pencil up from the top of the book case.
Walk back to the desk.
Place the pencil on top of the other pencil on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place two pencils on a desk.

high_descs: Walk over to the bookshelf on the opposite side of the room.
Pick up a pencil from the small stand to the right of the bookshelf.
Turn right and face the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk in front of the computer chair.
Turn around and walk to the door, then turn right and face the bookshelf.
Take the pencil from the top of the bookshelf.
Turn right and walk to the desk.
Put the pencil on top of the other pencil already on the desk at a ninety degree angle,  leaning against the box of tissues.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the desk.
